Additional licensing notices notes associated with subroutines
included in this code base
===============================================================

DMiLay
======

 This routine is from 
   Toon, O. and T. Ackerman, Applied Optics 20, 3657 (1981)

LPMNS, LPN, CHGM, GAMMA
=======================

   These routines are copyrighted by Shanjie Zhang and Jianming Jin.
   They have given permission to incorporate these routines into a
   user program provided that the copyright is acknowledged.

Numerical Recipes
=================

   This code base also includes a couple of routines that use the
   algorithms descriped in W.H. Press et al. 1986, 'Numerical Recipes'
   Cambridge University Press, (ISBN 0-521-30811).

   ludcmp, lubksb, gauleg, gamln, spline, splint